# v2.0.0 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Release with code used for CloneTracer bioaRxiv pre-print https://www.biorxiv.org/content/10.1101/2022.08.29.505648v1. Changes:
  
    - Fixes on Bayesian model
    - Updated vignettes and documentation


# v1.0.0 -----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  Initial release which contains:

    - Bayesian model for clonal assignments
    - Pipelines to process nuclear SNV and mitochondrial libraries
    - Scripts to design primers for amplification of nuclear SNVs from 10x 3' scRNAseq libraries
